#: of qteasy.database.DataSource.export_table_data:1
msgid ""
"将数据表中的数据读取出来之后导出到一个文件中，便于用户使用过程中小规模转移数据"
"或察看数据"
msgstr ""
"After reading the data from the data table, export it to a file, making it "
"convenient for users to transfer small amounts of data or view data during "
"use."

#: of qteasy.database.DataSource.export_table_data:3
msgid ""
"使用这个函数时，用户可以不用理会数据源的类型，只需要指定数据表名称，以及筛选条"
"件即可 导出的数据会被保存为csv文件，用户可以自行指定文件名以及文件存储路径，如"
"果不指定文件名， 则默认使用数据表名称作为文件名，如果不指定文件存储路径，则默"
"认使用当前工作目录作为 文件存储路径"
msgstr ""
"When using this function, users do not need to care about the type of data "
"source. They only need to specify the table name and filter conditions. The "
"exported data will be saved as a CSV file. Users can specify the file name "
"and storage path themselves. If no file name is specified, the table name is "
"used as the default file name. If no storage path is specified, the current "
"working directory is used as the default storage path."

#: of qteasy.database.DataSource.export_table_data:8
#: qteasy.database.DataSource.get_data_table_size:3
#: qteasy.database.DataSource.get_sys_table_last_id:3
#: qteasy.database.DataSource.get_table_info:7
#: qteasy.database.DataSource.read_table_data:5
