msgstr "Table name"

#: of qteasy.database.DataSource.export_table_data:10
msgid "导出的文件名，如果不指定，则默认使用数据表名称作为文件名"
msgstr ""
"Exported file name. If not specified, the table name is used as the file name "
"by default"

#: of qteasy.database.DataSource.export_table_data:12
msgid "导出的文件存储路径，如果不指定，则默认使用当前工作目录作为文件存储路径"
msgstr ""
"Storage path for the exported file. If not specified, the current working "
"directory is used by default as the file storage path."

#: of qteasy.database.DataSource.export_table_data:14
msgid "ts_code筛选条件，为空时给出所有记录"
msgstr "ts_code filter condition; if empty, all records are returned"

#: of qteasy.database.DataSource.export_table_data:16
#: qteasy.database.DataSource.read_table_data:9
msgid "YYYYMMDD格式日期，为空时不筛选"
msgstr "Date in YYYYMMDD format; if empty, no filtering is applied"

#: of qteasy.database.DataSource.export_table_data:18
#: qteasy.database.DataSource.read_table_data:11
msgid "YYYYMMDD格式日期，当start不为空时有效，筛选日期范围"
msgstr ""
"Date in YYYYMMDD format. Effective when start is not empty; used to filter "
"the date range."

#: of qteasy.database.DataSource.export_table_data:21
msgid "**file_path_name** -- 导出的文件的完整路径"
msgstr "**file_path_name** -- Full path of the exported file"

#: of qteasy.database.DataSource.get_all_basic_table_data:1
msgid ""
"一个快速获取所有basic数据表的函数，通常情况缓存处理以加快速度 如果设置"
"refresh_cache为True，则清空缓存并重新下载数据"
msgstr ""
"A function to quickly retrieve all basic data tables. Typically, caching is "
"used to speed things up. If refresh_cache is set to True, the cache is "
"cleared and the data is downloaded again."

#: of qteasy.database.DataSource.get_all_basic_table_data:4
msgid "如果为True，则清空缓存并重新下载数据"
msgstr "If True, clear the cache and re-download the data."

#: of qteasy.database.DataSource.get_all_basic_table_data:6
msgid "如果为True，则在数据表为空时抛出ValueError"
msgstr "If True, raise ValueError when the data table is empty."

#: of qteasy.database.DataSource.get_data_table_size:1
msgid "获取数据表占用磁盘空间的大小"
msgstr "Get the amount of disk space used by the data table."

#: of qteasy.database.DataSource.get_data_table_size:5
msgid "True时显示容易阅读的形式，如1.5MB而不是1590868， False时返回字节数"
msgstr ""
"When True, display in an easy-to-read format, such as 1.5MB instead of "
"1590868; when False, return the number of bytes."

#: of qteasy.database.DataSource.get_data_table_size:7
msgid "True时以字符串形式返回结果，便于打印"
msgstr "When True, return the result as a string for easier printing"

#: of qteasy.database.DataSource.get_data_table_size:10
msgid "**tuple (size, rows)**"
msgstr "**tuple (size, rows)**"

#: of qteasy.database.DataSource.get_sys_table_last_id:1
msgid "从已有的table中获取最后一个id"
msgstr "Get the last ID from an existing table"

#: of qteasy.database.DataSource.get_sys_table_last_id:6
msgid "**last_id**"
msgstr "**last_id**"

#: of qteasy.database.DataSource.get_table_data_coverage:1
msgid "获取本地数据表内容的覆盖范围，取出数据表的\"column\"列中的去重值并返回"
msgstr ""
"Get the coverage range of the local data table content: retrieve the "
"deduplicated values from the table’s \"column\" column and return them."

#: of qteasy.database.DataSource.get_table_data_coverage:3
msgid "数据表的名称"
msgstr "Name of the data table"

#: of qteasy.database.DataSource.get_table_data_coverage:5
msgid "需要去重并返回的数据列"
msgstr "Data columns that need to be deduplicated and returned"

#: of qteasy.database.DataSource.get_table_data_coverage:7
msgid ""
"为True时不需要返回整个数据列，仅返回最大值和最小值 如果仅返回最大值和和最小"
"值，返回值为一个包含两个元素的列表， 第一个元素是最小值，第二个是最大值，第三"
"个是总数量"
msgstr ""
"When True, there is no need to return the entire data column; only return the "
"maximum and minimum values. If only the maximum and minimum values are "
"returned, the return value is a list containing two elements: the first "
"element is the minimum value, the second is the maximum value, and the third "
"is the total count."

#: of qteasy.database.DataSource.get_table_info:1
msgid ""
"获取并打印数据表的相关信息，包括数据表是否已有数据，数据量大小，占用磁盘空间、"
"数据覆盖范围，"
msgstr ""
"Retrieve and print information about the table, including whether it already "
"contains data, the data volume, disk space usage, and data coverage range,"

#: of qteasy.database.DataSource.get_table_info:2
msgid "以及数据下载方法"
msgstr "and the data download method"

#: of qteasy.database.DataSource.get_table_info:5
msgid "Parameters:"
msgstr "Parameters"

#: of qteasy.database.DataSource.get_table_info:6
msgid "table: str"
msgstr "table: str"

#: of qteasy.database.DataSource.get_table_info:8
msgid "verbose: bool, Default: True"
msgstr "verbose: bool, Default: True"

#: of qteasy.database.DataSource.get_table_info:9
msgid "是否显示更多信息，如是，显示表结构等信息"
msgstr ""
"Whether to display more information; if so, show the table schema and other "
"details."

#: of qteasy.database.DataSource.get_table_info:10
msgid "print_info: bool, Default: True"
msgstr "print_info: bool, Default: True"

#: of qteasy.database.DataSource.get_table_info:11
msgid "是否打印输出所有结果"
msgstr "Whether to print all results."

#: of qteasy.database.DataSource.get_table_info:12
msgid "human: bool, Default: True"
msgstr "human: bool, Default: True"

#: of qteasy.database.DataSource.get_table_info:13
msgid "是否给出容易阅读的字符串形式"
msgstr "Whether to provide an easy-to-read string representation."

#: of qteasy.database.DataSource.get_table_info
msgid "returns"
msgstr "Returns"

#: of qteasy.database.DataSource.get_table_info:15
msgid "*一个dict，包含数据表的结构化信息：*"
msgstr "*A dict containing structured information about the data table:*"

#: of qteasy.database.DataSource.get_table_info:16
msgid ""
"*{* -- table name:    1, str, 数据表名称 table_exists:  2, bool，数据表是否存"
"在 table_size:    3, int/str，数据表占用磁盘空间，human 为True时返回容易阅读的"
"字符串 table_rows:    4, int/str，数据表的行数，human 为True时返回容易阅读的字"
"符串 primary_key1:  5, str，数据表第一个主键名称 pk_count1:     6, int，数据表"
"第一个主键记录数量 pk_min1:       7, obj，数据表主键1起始记录 pk_max1:       "
"8, obj，数据表主键2最终记录 primary_key2:  9, str，数据表第二个主键名称 "
"pk_count2:     10, int，数据表第二个主键记录 pk_min2:       11, obj，数据表主"
"键2起始记录 pk_max2:       12, obj，数据表主键2最终记录"
msgstr ""
"*{* -- table name:    1, str, table name table_exists:  2, bool, whether the "
"table exists table_size:    3, int/str, disk space used by the table; when "
"human is True, returns an easy-to-read string table_rows:    4, int/str, "
"number of rows in the table; when human is True, returns an easy-to-read "
"string primary_key1:  5, str, name of the first primary key pk_count1:     6, "
"int, record count for the first primary key pk_min1:       7, obj, starting "
"record of primary key 1 pk_max1:       8, obj, ending record of primary key 2 "
"primary_key2:  9, str, name of the second primary key pk_count2:     10, int, "
"record count for the second primary key pk_min2:       11, obj, starting "
"record of primary key 2 pk_max2:       12, obj, ending record of primary key 2"

#: of qteasy.database.DataSource.get_table_info:28
msgid "*}*"
msgstr "*}*"

#: of qteasy.database.DataSource.info:1
msgid "格式化打印database对象的各种主要信息"
msgstr "Format and print various key information about the database object"

#: of qteasy.database.DataSource.insert_sys_table_data:1
msgid "插入系统操作表的数据"
msgstr "Insert data into the system operations table."

#: of qteasy.database.DataSource.insert_sys_table_data:3
msgid ""
"一次插入一条记录，数据以dict形式给出 不需要给出数据的ID，因为ID会自动生成 如果"
"给出的数据字段不完整，则抛出异常 如果给出的数据中有不可用的字段，则抛出异常"
msgstr ""
"Insert one record at a time; the data is provided as a dict. You do not need "
"to provide the data ID, because the ID will be generated automatically. If "
"the provided data fields are incomplete, an exception is raised. If the "
"provided data contains unavailable fields, an exception is raised."

#: of qteasy.database.DataSource.insert_sys_table_data:8
#: qteasy.database.DataSource.update_sys_table_data:7
msgid "需要更新的数据表名称"
msgstr "Name of the table to update"

#: of qteasy.database.DataSource.insert_sys_table_data:10
msgid "需要更新或插入的数据，数据的key必须与数据库表的字段相同，否则会抛出异常"
msgstr ""
"Data to update or insert. The keys in the data must match the fields in the "
"database table; otherwise, an exception will be thrown."

#: of qteasy.database.DataSource.insert_sys_table_data:13
msgid "**record_id** -- 更新的记录ID"
msgstr "**record_id** -- ID of the record to update"

#: of qteasy.database.DataSource.insert_sys_table_data:16
msgid "当给出的字段不完整或者有不可用的字段时:"
msgstr "When the provided fields are incomplete or contain unavailable fields:"

#: of qteasy.database.DataSource.none_sys_tables:1
msgid "获取所有非系统数据表的清单"
msgstr "Get a list of all non-system tables"

#: of qteasy.database.DataSource.overview:1
msgid "以表格形式列出所有数据表的当前数据状态"
msgstr "List the current data status of all data tables in tabular form"

#: of qteasy.database.DataSource.overview:3
msgid "指定要列出的数据表，如果为None则列出所有数据表"
msgstr "Specify the data tables to list. If None, list all data tables."

#: of qteasy.database.DataSource.overview:5
msgid "是否打印数据表总揽"
msgstr "Whether to print a table overview"

#: of qteasy.database.DataSource.overview:7
msgid "是否包含系统表"
msgstr "Whether to include system tables"

#: of qteasy.database.DataSource.read_cached_table_data:1
msgid "缓存数据表数据以缩短读取速度，这个函数用于加快本地提取数据时加速"
msgstr ""
"Cache data table data to reduce read time. This function is used to speed up "
"local data extraction."

#: of qteasy.database.DataSource.read_cached_table_data:3
msgid ""
"在用户使用DataType对象大量读取数据时，通常需要重复从同一张数据表中以同样的参数"
"获取数据 为了提升读取速度，可以将数据表的数据缓存到内存中，以减少读取时间，但"
"在正常的数据表操作中 并不适合使用缓存，因为数据表通常需要实时刷新，因此本函数"
"仅供DataType对象读取数据使用"
msgstr ""
"When a user uses a DataType object to read large amounts of data, it is "
"usually necessary to repeatedly fetch data from the same table with the same "
"parameters. To improve read speed, you can cache the table data in memory to "
"reduce read time. However, in normal table operations, caching is not "
"suitable because tables usually need to be refreshed in real time. Therefore, "
"this function is only for DataType objects to use when reading data."

#: of qteasy.database.DataSource.read_sys_table_data:1
msgid "读取系统操作表的数据，包括读取所有记录，以及根据给定的条件读取记录"
msgstr ""
"Read data from the system operations table, including reading all records and "
"reading records based on the given conditions."

#: of qteasy.database.DataSource.read_sys_table_data:3
msgid "返回的数据类型为pd.DataFrame，如果给出kwargs，返回根据条件筛选后的数据"
msgstr ""
"The returned data type is pd.DataFrame. If kwargs are provided, return the "
"data filtered according to the conditions."

#: of qteasy.database.DataSource.read_sys_table_data:5
#: qteasy.database.DataSource.read_sys_table_record:6
msgid "需要读取的数据表名称"
msgstr "Name of the data table to read."

#: of qteasy.database.DataSource.read_sys_table_data:7
msgid "筛选数据的条件，包括用作筛选条件的字典如: {account_id = 123}"
msgstr ""
"Conditions for filtering data, including a dictionary used as filter "
"criteria, e.g.: {account_id = 123}."

#: of qteasy.database.DataSource.read_sys_table_data:10
msgid "返回的数据为DataFrame，如果给出kwargs，返回的数据仅包括筛选后的数据"
msgstr ""
"The returned data is a DataFrame. If kwargs are provided, the returned data "
"includes only the filtered data."

#: of qteasy.database.DataSource.read_sys_table_record:1
msgid "读取系统操作表的数据，根据指定的id读取数据，返回一个dict"
msgstr ""
"Read data from the system operations table. Read data by the specified id and "
"return a dict."

#: of qteasy.database.DataSource.read_sys_table_record:3
msgid ""
"本函数调用read_sys_table_data()读取整个数据表，并返回record_id行的数据 返回的"
"dict包含所有字段的值，key为字段名，value为字段值"
msgstr ""
"This function calls read_sys_table_data() to read the entire table and "
"returns the data for the record_id row. The returned dict contains the values "
"of all fields, where the key is the field name and the value is the field "
"value."

#: of qteasy.database.DataSource.read_sys_table_record:8
msgid "需要读取的数据的id"
msgstr "ID of the data to read."

#: of qteasy.database.DataSource.read_sys_table_record:10
msgid "筛选数据的条件，包括用作筛选条件的字典如: account_id = 123"
msgstr ""
"Filtering conditions, including a dictionary used as filter criteria, e.g.: "
"account_id = 123"

#: of qteasy.database.DataSource.read_sys_table_record:13
msgid "**data** -- 读取的数据，包括数据表的结构化信息以及数据表中的记录"
msgstr ""
"**data** -- The data read, including the table’s schema information and the "
"records in the table."

#: of qteasy.database.DataSource.read_table_data:1
msgid ""
"从本地数据表中读取数据并返回DataFrame，不修改数据格式，primary_key为DataFrame"
"的index"
msgstr ""
"Read data from a local table and return a DataFrame without modifying the "
"data format; primary_key is used as the DataFrame index."

#: of qteasy.database.DataSource.read_table_data:3
msgid ""
"在读取数据表时读取所有的列，但是返回值筛选ts_code以及trade_date between start "
"和 end"
msgstr ""
"When reading the table, read all columns, but in the return value filter by "
"ts_code and trade_date between start and end."

#: of qteasy.database.DataSource.read_table_data:7
msgid "ts_code筛选条件，逗号分隔字符串，为空时给出所有记录"
msgstr ""
"ts_code filter condition: a comma-separated string. If empty, all records are "
"returned."

#: of qteasy.database.DataSource.read_table_data:13
msgid ""
"是否将primary key设置为DataFrame的index 如果为False，primary key将作为普通的列"
"返回，此时DataFrame的index为默认的整数index"
msgstr ""
"Whether to set the primary key as the DataFrame index. If False, the primary "
"key will be returned as a regular column, and the DataFrame index will be the "
"default integer index."

